value.name: Foster parents from Adams indicted following 10-month-old's death
value.description: Matthew Tucker, 37, and Cassandra Barlow-Tucker, 37, were charged with manslaughter and reckless endangerment of a child on April 8, the Berkshire County District Attorney's Office has said.
